---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout
  title="PulseStack Features – AI-Powered Insight"
  description="Explore how PulseStack turns raw feedback into a prioritized roadmap."
>
  
  <!-- FEATURES -->
  <section class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-4 py-16 space-y-10">
    <div class="max-w-2xl space-y-3">
      <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-slate-50">
        All your customer signal, finally working together.
      </h1>
      <p class="text-sm md:text-base text-slate-300">
        PulseStack ingests every piece of feedback, finds the patterns using AI, and surfaces exactly what deserves your team’s attention.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="grid gap-6 md:grid-cols-3">
      <div class="rounded-2xl border border-slate-800 bg-slate-900/60 p-5 space-y-2">
        <h2 class="text-sm font-medium text-slate-50">AI-powered insight clustering</h2>
        <p class="text-xs text-slate-300">
          Automatically groups similar feedback across tools, detects emerging topics, and scores them by estimated revenue and churn impact.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="rounded-2xl border border-slate-800 bg-slate-900/60 p-5 space-y-2">
        <h2 class="text-sm font-medium text-slate-50">Unified feedback hub</h2>
        <p class="text-xs text-slate-300">
          Support tickets, churn reasons, NPS responses, sales notes, and app reviews in one, queryable workspace built for product teams.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="rounded-2xl border border-slate-800 bg-slate-900/60 p-5 space-y-2">
        <h2 class="text-sm font-medium text-slate-50">Roadmap impact simulation</h2>
        <p class="text-xs text-slate-300">
          Run scenarios to see how shipping specific initiatives is likely to move NPS, expansion revenue, and churn over time.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- HOW IT WORKS -->
  <section class="border-t border-slate-800 bg-slate-950/80">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-4 py-16 space-y-10">
      <div class="max-w-2xl space-y-3">
        <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-slate-50">
          From raw noise to a roadmap your team can trust.
        </h2>
        <p class="text-sm md:text-base text-slate-300">
          PulseStack connects to the tools you already use and turns unstructured feedback into clear, prioritized initiatives.
        </p>
      </div>
      <ol class="grid gap-6 md:grid-cols-3 text-sm">
        <li class="rounded-2xl border border-slate-800 bg-slate-900/60 p-5 space-y-2">
          <span class="inline-flex h-7 w-7 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-indigo-500/20 text-xs text-indigo-300">1</span>
          <h3 class="font-medium text-slate-50">Connect your existing stack</h3>
          <p class="text-xs text-slate-300">
            One-click integrations with tools like Zendesk, Intercom, HubSpot, Linear, and Segment — plus API access for anything custom.
          </p>
        </li>
        <li class="rounded-2xl border border-slate-800 bg-slate-900/60 p-5 space-y-2">
          <span class="inline-flex h-7 w-7 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-indigo-500/20 text-xs text-indigo-300">2</span>
          <h3 class="font-medium text-slate-50">Let AI analyze the signal</h3>
          <p class="text-xs text-slate-300">
            Our models detect themes, sentiments, and impact drivers, then continuously update as new feedback streams in.
          </p>
        </li>
        <li class="rounded-2xl border border-slate-800 bg-slate-900/60 p-5 space-y-2">
          <span class="inline-flex h-7 w-7 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-indigo-500/20 text-xs text-indigo-300">3</span>
          <h3 class="font-medium text-slate-50">Align your roadmap and ship</h3>
          <p class="text-xs text-slate-300">
            Share insight boards with stakeholders, export initiatives into your delivery tools, and track impact over time.
          </p>
        </li>
      </ol>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
